solver.distributedMemory.scheduling

Class ClusterMutExclNonPipelined.OptimizeSchedule

  • java.lang.Object
    • solver.distributedMemory.scheduling.ClusterMutExclNonPipelined.OptimizeSchedule
  • Enclosing class:
    ClusterMutExclNonPipelined

    private class ClusterMutExclNonPipelined.OptimizeSchedule
extends java.lang.Object
    Schedule optimizer to improve latency and processor usage. We use another instance of ClusterMutExclNonPipelined class in order to generate only a few constraints in addition to new non-lazy and processor optimizing constraints to solve the problem.
    Author:
    Pranav Tendulkar
